.SH EXAMPLES
.IP \[bu] 2
Select the record that the age field value greater than (with using $gt) 10
under the collection, bar, and add (with using $inc) one to the age field.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
>\ db.foo.bar.find(\ {\ age:\ {\ $gt:\ 10\ }\ }\ ).update(\ {\ $inc:\ {\ age:\ 1\ }\ },\ true\ )
